title: Complete coverage: Notre Dame's Coco Chen, Logan Lencheski capture district title
text:
Logan Lencheski, left, and Coco Chen of Notre Dame won the District 11 Class AA tennis doubles title on Monday. (Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com) By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 20, 2015 12:48 PM, updated October 20, 2015 2:46 PM 
Notre Dame senior Coco Chen and freshman Logan Lencheski outlasted Bethlehem Catholic 's Brenna Magliochetti and Molly Ehrig in a classic three-set match to win the District 11 Class AA doubles title on Monday at Lehigh University. 
It was the first district girls tennis title for Notre Dame.
